{"tid":1874494,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"德甲新星嚮往利物浦　5.1億到手","createTime":"2020-02-11T08:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T10:49:17.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fad3ce24c7cee52a204d01bb60a8ec7f4b4fcb6f","tid":1874494,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:42:39.000Z","msg":"利物浦打響個朵，依家選擇多多，除咗菲臘比古天奴同利華古遜嘅夏維斯，RB萊比錫23歲前鋒迪姆華拿又話想踢利物浦！英國傳媒《Athletic》報道，呢位德國國腳違約金係5100萬鎊(約5.1億港元)，相當抵買。<br />\n<br />\n迪姆華拿今季德甲表現出色，上陣29場入25球及10個助攻，由於表現超班，圈內人預計萊比錫留唔住佢，一般估計佢嘅身價會繼續上升，現時嘅違約金係5100萬鎊，不過如果佢喺今夏歐國盃有突出表現，轉會費就唔止呢個數，所以有買趁早。德國《圖片報》報道，迪姆華拿對利物浦甚為嚮往。<br />\n<br />\n至於另一對利物浦有利嘅係，佢哋剛於冬窗向薩爾斯堡買入南野拓實，依家再向同屬紅牛系嘅萊比錫買球員，作為舊客戶嘅紅軍喺運作上會更順利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20200211061623461-0211_00882_001&amp;whichpage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2Fnewe%2Findex.html%3FarticleId%3Dbkn-20200211061623461-0211_00882_001%26whichpage%3D1&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yCK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=af6c1ae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://football.on.cc/cnt/news/newe/index.html?articleId=bkn-20200211061623461-0211_00882_001&amp;whichpage=1</a>"},{"pid":"d548b384b35d1e2340dff781ea82e763363592ec","tid":1874494,"uid":119729,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:48:46.000Z","msg":"紅牛 - 利記二隊<br />\n基達, 拓實, 雲拿"},{"pid":"2484f36a0d7bab849296a63d1511a9e1fb10517c","tid":1874494,"uid":18395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T08:51:23.000Z","msg":"Go mu la diu"},{"pid":"ca2a48d936d131cb58e6788311ed7da1ccc8eee1","tid":1874494,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"佢都新星？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056c77e6119f7b25ab574ea524462d45a06777ca","tid":1874494,"uid":72334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T09:08:23.000Z","msg